      "role": "user",
      "content": "got it. i'll be careful. i was just worried about something being active down in the dirt, like something eating through the roots or making a mess of the soil structure. is it common for stuff to happen underground that you can't see from the surface until the plant starts dying?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
